==English==
===Noun===
'''rubbernecker''' (''Plural:'' '''rubberneckers''')

#Someone who watchs, a [[spectator]], in the sense that they [[crane]] their neck as though it were made of [[rubber]].  Especially those who watch [[accident]]s.
#:''The minor accident caused a traffic jam as '''rubberneckers''' slowed down to get a good view of the battered cars.''